window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Love had cut me in so many ways I wondered if my heart could take any more. </b></p> <p>But then I saw him. He was my boss. A single father.&nbsp;</p> <p>And to top it off he was insolent.&nbsp;</p> <p>I didn’t intend to want him, that wasn’t my objective. But somehow I couldn’t say no.&nbsp;</p> <p>We shouldn’t have worked, but like witchcraft, I was under his spell.&nbsp;</p> <p>My heart’s been destroyed before. I’m not sure it can handle heartbreak again.</p>"; 
